manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Ultra Slim 4-Port USB 3.0 Data Hub Turn one of your computer’s USB ports into 4 for your device charging and data management. Widely used in mouse, keyboard, U disk, card reader, hard disk, printer, desktop fan and other devices with USB interface.

5Gbps Data Transfer The USB 3.0 interface supports 5Gbps super-speed transmission, which can transfer a 1G movie in 3 seconds, and supports fast mutual transfer of files between 2 hard drives, without waiting for file transfer.

Support mainstream systems This USB Hub Supports Windows 10, 8, 7, Vista, XP, Mac OSx 10.6-10.12 or later, Linux 2.6.14 or Later. High performance chip Each function is equipped with an independent chip to ensure stable connection and no lag. LED Indicator light Blue LED to indicate the working status of this USB 3.0 hub. Compact and Lightweight Ultra slim design avoids clutter and leaving room for all the accessories you’ll insert. Easy to carry around.

Support 4 USB port work at same time Supports 4 USB ports to work at the same time, which solves the problem of insufficient USB ports on your computer or notebook, and also avoid repeated plugging and unplugging,protect the computer's native interfaces. No Delay, No Freeze It supports 5Gbps high-speed data transmission, and the transmission speed is 10 times that of USB2.0. It is responsive when connected to a mouse and keyboard to play games, without delay or lag. Wide Application Applicable to all kinds of devices with USB interface, such as: mouse, keyboard, U disk, electric fan, hard disk, printer and so on.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 2, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the VIENON 4-Port USB 3.0 Hub and I couldn't be happier with my purchase! This hub has proven to be an invaluable addition to my setup.First and foremost, the build quality is exceptional. The hub feels sturdy and well-made, giving me confidence that it will last for a long time. The compact size is also a major plus, making it easy to carry around or tuck away on my desk without taking up much space.The USB 3.0 speeds are impressive. I've noticed a significant improvement in data transfer rates compared to my previous hub. Whether I'm transferring large files or connecting multiple devices, everything works seamlessly and without any lag or delay.One of the standout features for me is the thoughtful design. The ports are well-spaced, allowing for easy and convenient plug-ins without crowding or interfering with adjacent connections. This has made a noticeable difference when using bulkier USB devices.I also appreciate the LED indicator lights, which provide a clear visual confirmation that the hub is active and working. It's a small touch, but it's these little details that demonstrate VIENON's attention to quality and user experience.Lastly, the affordability of this hub is a major selling point. Considering the level of performance and reliability it offers, it's an outstanding value for the price.In summary, the VIENON 4-Port USB 3.0 Hub has exceeded my expectations in every way. It's a reliable, well-designed, and high-performing device that has made a positive impact on my workflow. I highly recommend it to anyone in need of a top-notch USB hub!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I’ve had this product for a week now and so far so good. It’s as easy as plug and play and it works instantly. So far I have my keyboard, mouse, speaker, ring light, LED mousepad, and webcam plugged in with no issues. I like that there’s a light to indicate there’s power running through. My only con so far is that I wish the cord was about an inch or two longer. It feels cheap and very light, but like I said it’s getting the job done and running everything I plug into it. I’ll update if there are any issues I run into.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love this little hub
reviews.reviewText: This is an awesome little USB hub if you need a few extra USB ports on a computer. I have it attached to the lid of my laptop, so it's always in reach and still out of the way. It's the perfect way to plug in my mouse receiver as well as any other USB cables I need to use without needing to search both sides of my laptop to find an open port. It's thin enough to not get in the way when the laptop lid is closed, and all of the ports are easily accessible.
